    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Evercore 的 Emanuel 警告称，市场将出现“过度调整”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-11/evercore-s-emanuel-warns-of-exuberant-corrections-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Evercore ISI 股票、衍生品和量化策略高级董事总经理朱利安·伊曼纽尔 (Julian Emanuel) 认为，随着估值接近过去 60 年来的最高水平，明年市场将面临来自不完美消息的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-11/evercore-s-emanuel-warns-of-exuberant-corrections-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 12:13:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
