      <title>中国转向巴西 特朗普贸易战将对美国农民造成更大伤害</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/trump-trade-war-to-hurt-us-farmers-more-as-china-turns-to-brazil</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普发起的第一次贸易战给美国大豆种植户造成了 110 亿美元的损失。后续影响必定会更严重。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/trump-trade-war-to-hurt-us-farmers-more-as-china-turns-to-brazil</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国银行警告股市低估通胀回归风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/inflation-reading-matters-more-than-the-equity-market-is-showing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[虽然抗通胀的斗争可能基本取得了胜利，但价格压力带来的紧张局势仍可能破坏人们对降息的信心。股市似乎对这些警告视而不见。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/inflation-reading-matters-more-than-the-equity-market-is-showing</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 08:13:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>黄金价格上涨，因交易员预测美国通胀数据</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/gold-holds-advance-as-traders-count-down-to-us-inflation-figures</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易商为美国通胀数据做准备，黄金价格连续三天上涨，这将有助于确定美联储在下周的今年最后一次会议上是降息还是维持利率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/gold-holds-advance-as-traders-count-down-to-us-inflation-figures</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 00:39:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场综述：中国可能允许人民币贬值 报告推动美元上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[有报道称，中国领导人正考虑允许人民币贬值，以应对唐纳德·特朗普第二次担任总统后征收更高的关税，此后美元走强。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 22:29:47 GMT</pubDate>
